import PyPDF2
pdf_path = '/workspace/benchmark/datasets/16-KnowProb/KnowProb-main/paper.pdf'
with open(pdf_path, 'rb') as f:
    reader = PyPDF2.PdfReader(f)
    num_pages = len(reader.pages)
    first_page = reader.pages[0].extract_text()
    last_page = reader.pages[-1].extract_text()
    sample_pages = [reader.pages[i].extract_text() for i in range(min(5, num_pages))]
num_pages, first_page[:500], last_page[:500], sample_pages
